'''Witch's House''' is a quest involving a [[boy]] whose ball had been lost in the garden of an unpleasant local witch, [[Nora T. Hagg]]. The adventurer is asked to retrieve it, having to figure out how to proceed in [[witch's house (location)|Nora's house]] along the way.

==Details==
{{Quest details
|start = Talk to the [[boy]] near the gate entrance of [[Taverley]].
|startmap = 2928,3456
|difficulty = Intermediate
|description = A young boy who lives in Taverley has kicked his ball into the garden of a scary old lady.

He asks you to get it back for him. This proves more difficult than it first sounds.
|length = Very Short
|requirements = * The ability to defeat 4 monsters from level 19 to 53 without a break.
|items = *[[Cheese]] (You may wish to bring several in case you mess up. One source is in [[Draynor Village]] - [[Aggie]]'s house)
*[[Leather gloves]] (obtainable during the quest)
|recommended = * {{SCP|Combat|35|link=yes}}
* [[Weapon]], [[armour]] and some [[food]]
* 4 free inventory slots
|kills = *[[Witch's experiment]] ''(level 19, 30, 42 and 53)''
|leagueRegion = <poem>
{{RE|Asgarnia}} — location requirement
</poem>
}}

==Walkthrough==
===Getting started===
{{Map|name=Boy|x=2928|y=3456|r=3|align=left|width=240|height=240|mtype=square|caption=The start point of the quest.}}
[[File:Witch's House - Boy.png|thumb|220px|Talking to the [[boy]].]]
Go to [[Taverley]] and talk to the [[boy]] near the eastern entrance to Taverley along the hedges. He says that he kicked his [[ball]] over the hedge into the garden and the [[Nora T. Hagg|witch]] living in the house put it in her shed. The boy wants you to get it back for him. Tell him you'll see what you can do.

===Breaking in===
[[File:Witch's House - Breaking in.png|thumb|220px|The location of the [[Door key (Witch's House)|key]].]]
Go west then north around the hedge to the front door of the house - it is locked. Look-under the pot north of the door to find a [[Door key (Witch's House)|door key]] and enter the house. Read the entire [[Diary (Witch's House)|diary]] on the table.

===Getting to the garden===
Go down the ladder in the northern room to enter the basement. If you don't already have [[leather gloves]], search the [[boxes (witch's house)|boxes]] for a pair, however it may take many attempts to find them. Equip your gloves, go through the [[gate (witch's house)|gate]], and search the [[cupboard (witch's house)|cupboard]] for the [[Magnet (Witch's House)|magnet]]. Go back up the ladder and into the southern room with the door that leads to garden. '''''Note: Be quick, the mouse will go away after some time, you will lose your cheese and have to get another one.''''' Drop your [[cheese]], OR use the cheese on the mouse hole if dropping it does not work. Suddenly, a [[Mouse (Witch's House)|mouse]] will come out; use the magnet on the mouse and it will unlock the door. Enter the door into the garden.

The following gloves must be used to open the gate and to avoid taking damage: 
